                  <run>Filter: Performance KPI: Filter to use when showing the performance of a KPI for a given month</run>
                </formatted-text>
              </desc>
            </column>
            <column caption='Period: Months to Current Month' datatype='integer' name='[LinPack_782981515852570131]' role='dimension' type='quantitative'>
              <calculation class='tableau' formula='-1*(([Parameters].[LinPack_661713406488724115]- [LinPack_112320563205440314])*12+([Parameters].[LinPack_268298139370622864] - [LinPack_923155276951376517]))' />
              <desc>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run>Period: Months to Current Month: Returns the number of Months between the selected Current Month and the reference date of the data source</run>
                </formatted-text>
              </desc>
