            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontsize='7' italic='true'><![CDATA[    Shows how much each <[Parameters].[pSelect Store or Business Line (copy)_845550866685894659]> contributed to Total Sales. The color of a circle indicates whether the sales of the <[Parameters].[pSelect Store or Business Line (copy)_845550866685894659]> have increased (blue) or decreased (orange), its size indicating the magnitude of the change.]]></run>
