        <zone h='94124' hidden-by-user='true' id='331' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='86735' x='13145' y='2880'>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='38364' hidden-by-user='true' id='332' type-v2='text' w='86615' x='13205' y='2995'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run fontcolor='#2b5c8a' fontsize='7' italic='true'>Follow us on Youtube for latest Accelerator videos: @TableauAccelerators </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#2b5c8a' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>RETAIL SALES</run>
              <run>
This Tableau Accelerator allows you to:
     - </run>
              <run bold='true'>Assess the performance of your network &amp; grow your sales</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>Æ     </run>
              <run>-</run>
              <run bold='true'> Predict evolution of sales</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>Æ     </run>
              <run>- </run>
              <run bold='true'>Optimize your product mix</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>Æ     </run>
              <run>- </run>
              <run bold='true'>Identify emerging/declining products</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>Æ     </run>
              <run>- </run>
              <run bold='true'>Pinpoint Stores that need help</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>Æ     </run>
              <run>- </run>
              <run bold='true'>Learn best practices from top stores</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>Æ     </run>
              <run>- </run>
              <run bold='true'>Identify sales drivers</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>Æ     </run>
              <run>- </run>
              <run bold='true'>Deep-dive at lowest level of detail: Store, Product Line, Product</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#2b5c8a' fontsize='10'>Answer key business questions</run>
              <run>
     - What the performance of the Network?
     - Which stores need support?
     - What are the emerging Products/Stores?
     - How do I perform in my store compared to similar other stores?

</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone h='24539' hidden-by-user='true' id='344' layout-strategy-id='distribute-evenly' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='86615' x='13205' y='41359'>
            <zone forceUpdate='true' h='24540' hidden-by-user='true' id='346' type-v2='text' w='43338' x='13205' y='41359'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#2b5c8a' fontsize='10'>Monitor and improve KPIs</run>
                <run>Æ&#10;  </run>
                <run fontcolor='#2b5c8a' italic='true' underline='true'>Sales</run>
                <run>&#10;     - </run>
                <run bold='true'>Total Sales</run>
                <run><![CDATA[: <[Parameters].[KPI_TotalSales_Calculation (copy)_306244822675111937]>
     - ]]></run>
                <run bold='true'>Sales per Store</run>
                <run><![CDATA[: <[Parameters].[KPI_TotalSales_Description (copy)_306244822678437890]>
  ]]></run>
                <run fontcolor='#2b5c8a' italic='true' underline='true'>Stores</run>
                <run>&#10;     - </run>
                <run bold='true'>Active Stores</run>
                <run><![CDATA[: <[Parameters].[KPI_TotalSales_Description (copy)_2301902412558700544]>
  ]]></run>
                <run fontcolor='#2b5c8a' italic='true' underline='true'>Products</run>
                <run>&#10;     - </run>
                <run bold='true'>Distinct Products Sold</run>
                <run><![CDATA[: <[Parameters].[KPI_ActiveStores_Description (copy)_2301902412558995459]>]]></run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone h='24540' hidden-by-user='true' id='345' type-v2='text' w='43277' x='56543' y='41359'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run bold='true' fontcolor='#2b5c8a' fontsize='10'>Required attributes</run>
                <run>&#10;     - </run>
                <run bold='true' underline='true'>Date</run>
                <run>Æ </run>
                <run italic='true'>(date</run>
                <run>): Sales date&#10;     - </run>
                <run bold='true' underline='true'>Store</run>
                <run>Æ </run>
                <run italic='true'>(string)</run>
                <run>: Store name&#10;     -</run>
                <run bold='true'> Store Type</run>
                <run>Æ </run>
                <run italic='true'>(string)</run>
                <run>: Store type&#10;     - </run>
                <run bold='true'>Country</run>
                <run>Æ </run>
                <run italic='true'>(string; role: country)</run>
                <run>: Country where the store is located
     - </run>
                <run bold='true'>State</run>
                <run>Æ </run>
                <run italic='true'>(String; role: province)</run>
                <run>: State where the store is located
     - </run>
                <run bold='true'>City</run>
                <run>Æ </run>
                <run italic='true'>(string; role: city)</run>
                <run>: City where the store is located
     -</run>
                <run bold='true'> Store Latitude</run>
                <run>Æ </run>
                <run italic='true'>(numeric)</run>
                <run>: Latitude where the store is located
     - </run>
                <run bold='true'>Store Longitude</run>
                <run>Æ </run>
                <run italic='true'>(numeric)</run>
                <run>: Longitude where the store is located
     - </run>
                <run bold='true' underline='true'>Product</run>
                <run>Æ </run>
                <run italic='true'>(string)</run>
                <run>: Product name&#10;     -</run>
                <run bold='true'> Product Line</run>
                <run>Æ </run>
                <run italic='true'>(string)</run>
                <run>: Product Line, Product Category, Business Line...
     - </run>
                <run bold='true'>Sales Amount</run>
                <run>Æ </run>
                <run italic='true'>(numeric)</run>
                <run>: Sales amount</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#2b5c8a' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='solid' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='1' />
            <format attr='background-color' value='#f5f5f5' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
