        <zone h='94124' hidden-by-user='true' id='338' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='82713' x='13145' y='2880'>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='70277' hidden-by-user='true' id='337' type-v2='text' w='82593' x='13205' y='2995'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run fontcolor='#2b5c8a' fontsize='7' italic='true'>All Tableau Accelerators can be found on Tableau Exchange:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#2b5c8a' fontsize='7' italic='true'>Æ </run>
              <run auto-url='true' fontcolor='#2b5c8a' fontsize='7' hyperlink='tabdoc:load-url url=&amp;quot;https://exchange.tableau.com/accelerators&amp;quot;' italic='true'>https://exchange.tableau.com/accelerators</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#2b5c8a' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='12'>RELATED ACCELERATORS</run>
              <run>
In addition to this Accelerator, you will probably be interested in other Tableau Accelerators in the same field:

</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#2b5c8a' fontsize='10'>Retail</run>
              <run>&#10;     - </run>
              <run bold='true'>Retail Sales</run>
              <run>: </run>
